超古い(ばてるってこと)コントローラーには許可している。<br /><br /><br />If the controller is really old and worn out (from having used it a LOT), it is possible to press up and down (or left and right) simultaneously.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=7">Quietust</a> — Wed Dec 21, 2005 8:39 pm</p><hr />
